dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Donald Cooper. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Donald. My name is Catherine Morris.
Lovely to meet you, Catherine. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Of course. It's five eight zero zero two.
Thank you, Catherine. Can you also confirm the make and model of your car for verification purposes?
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss today regarding your policy or coverage?
I just wanted to inquire about adding roadside assistance to my policy.
Certainly, Catherine. I can assist you with that. Thank you for reaching out. Is there anything else you need help with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Donald.
You're welcome, Catherine. Have a wonderful day. Goodbye.
